NAME
    split-string

DESCRIPTION
    Split a string returning the specified index (or last instance by default)

    This function requires [2] parameter(s) and [1] optional parameter

    REQUIRED PARAMETERS:
    	$1 - NEEDLE
    	$2 - HAYSTACK

	OPTIONAL PARAMETERS:
    	$3 - INDEX

SYNOPSIS
	Brackets [] indicate optional

EXAMPLES
    split-string NEEDLE HAYSTACK [INDEX] 

AVAILABLE OPTIONS:
    N/A